race.comment: RESOLUTE LADY (9) scored by a nose two back at this track then just missed the frame latest when fourth at Ipswich. Will appreciate the drop in the weights. Won't find this as tough and is likely to feature. BEE EXACT (18) doesn't win out of turn but was in the finish last time when beaten 0.6 lengths into second over 1200m here. Should be poised just off the lead and best figures should see him run well. TRISKELION (5) last start finished fifth at Murwillumbah over 1200m. Tackling a more suitable race this time so he will be hard to beat. GRAND CRUSADER (13) best of the rest with the claim from the low draw.
